Problem Statement :
Given a string S  and a character X, the task is to find the last index (0 based indexing) of X in string S. If no index found then the answer will be -1.
Input: S = "Geeks", P = 'e'
Output: 2

Problem Statement Link :
https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/last-index-of-a-character-in-the-string4516/1?page=1&category=Strings&difficulty=Basic,Easy&sortBy=submissions

Solution :
class Solution{
    int LastIndex(String s, char p)
    {
        for(int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--)
            if(s.charAt(i) == p)
                return (i);
        return -1;
    }
}
